  <brief_title>A Safety and Efficacy Study of Golimumab (CNTO 148) in Patients With Active Rheumatoid Arthritis Despite Methotrexate Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study of Golimumab (CNTO 148) Administered in Combination With Methotrexate (MTX) in Patients With Active Rheumatoid Arthritis</official_title>
